Blackpool have opened talks with former Arsenal winger Quincy Owusu-Abeyie. 

The Championship strugglers are continuing to piece together a squad with former Leeds striker El Hadji Diouf training with them also last week.

Owusu-Abeyie, 28, is a free agent after leaving Panathinaikos and is discussing a short-term contract.

